A vintage 1950s-style illustration of an overwhelmed office worker drowning in a sea of paper envelopes and manila folders, their arms reaching up from the chaos. The scene is rendered in muted mustard yellows, burnt oranges, and teal blues with halftone dot textures. Scattered around the figure are floating magnifying glasses and folder tabs creating a swirling vortex pattern. The desk beneath is barely visible under the avalanche of correspondence. The composition uses dramatic diagonal lines and retro advertising aesthetic with slightly exaggerated proportions and warm, aged paper tones throughout.
